      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Are you a fan of a good project? This car is a fantastic opportunity for someone who loves to get their hands dirty! While it's in poor condition and will need some significant mechanical and cosmetic work to get it back to its prime, it's an honest start for a restoration. This is your chance to bring a vehicle back to life at a budget-friendly price!",
